thread.title: georgesutton

author: georgesutton
title: georgesutton
text:
I have recently started using the Servcorp co-working area on level 35 of One International Towers in Barangaroo.
I found the Servcorp team there to be super enthusiastic and helpful right from my first call to enquire. They got an understanding of my needs and provided me with a very cost effective package which was important to me given this is a start up.
The location is great and the atmosphere in the shared area has a real buzz about it.
I have no hesitation in recommending this team and the Barangaroo building to others.
